        <mxCell id="zcgHoHAn1pPS7amRuiG0-2" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Final Practical&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Functional Requirements:&lt;/u&gt;&lt;br&gt;1) client should be able to register and login&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;2) client should be able to create post (text/image/video)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;3) clients should be able to follow each other&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;4) client should be able to like or comment on the post&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;5) client should be able to view feed of posts from users they follow&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Non-Functional Requirements:&lt;/u&gt;&lt;br&gt;1) Scalable : capable of handling 500M-700M DAU&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;2) CAP theorem : the system should always be available.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;3) low latency : 100ms&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;4) security : system should be secure&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
